methods.name: UnaryOpAssembler
methods.logic: Constructor for the UnaryOpAssembler class. Initializes the state_ property with the provided CodeAssemblerState.

methods.name: Generate_BitwiseNotWithFeedback
methods.logic: Generates code for the bitwise NOT operation with feedback. It takes the context, the value to negate, a slot for feedback, a feedback vector (if available), and an update mode for feedback.  It returns the result of the operation.

methods.name: Generate_DecrementWithFeedback
methods.logic: Generates code for the decrement operation with feedback. It takes the context, the value to decrement, a slot for feedback, a feedback vector (if available), and an update mode for feedback. It returns the result of the operation.

methods.name: Generate_IncrementWithFeedback
methods.logic: Generates code for the increment operation with feedback. It takes the context, the value to increment, a slot for feedback, a feedback vector (if available), and an update mode for feedback. It returns the result of the operation.

methods.name: Generate_NegateWithFeedback
methods.logic: Generates code for the negate operation with feedback. It takes the context, the value to negate, a slot for feedback, a feedback vector (if available), and an update mode for feedback.  It returns the result of the operation.
